          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The energy distribution obtained in the present  work",
                " contains most of the fast photoneutrons. It is shown",
                " that the neutron yield cannot  be  explained  within",
                " the statistical theory."
